// @max_count {Number} Max keywords.
// @max_length {Number} Max keyword length..
// @min_length {Number} Min keyword length.
// returns String Array;
```

Method creates an identifier from a string

```js
String.makeid();
// returns String;
```

Set maximum length of string.

```js
String.max(maxLength, [chars]);
// @maxLength {Number} Maximum length of string.
