// returns Object;
```

CSV parser.

```js
String.parseCSV([delimiter]);
// @delimiter {String} A value delimiter
// returns Array;
```

__CSV example:__

```
value1,value2,value3
value1,value2,value3
```

__Parsed output:__

```
