```

__Example__:

```
var builder = new ErrorBuilder();

instance.push('name', '@');
// Gets the description according to: instance.onResource('name');

instance.push('name');
// Gets the description according to: instance.onResource('name');

instance.add('name', '@name-minimum');
// Gets the description according to: instance.onResource('name-minimum');

// Skips getting of description from the resource:
instance.add('name', 'You has to enter your name.');

// Good to know
// Into the ErrorBuilder you can add another instance of ErrorBuilder
instance.push(new ErrorBuilder());
```

