We have prepared method `MAPSCHEMA()` in Total.js framework which can help you bind code-list values from DB directly to the schema.

```js
MAPSCHEMA(schema, [prop_pk]);
// @schema {String} a schema name, can contain multiple names separated by comma
// @prop_pk {String} optional, a primary key name, default: id
```

__Example__:

```js
// Schema definition:
// schema.define('gender', []);
// schema.define('currencyid', []);

// Usage
var db = DBMS();
