__Total.js Message Service__ (TMS) contains Publish/Subscribe pattern that allows you to integrate multiple Total.js apps and much more accessible than ever before. __TMS__ is built on top of [__JSON schemas__](http://json-schema.org).

- [Download __TMS Integrator app__](/tms/daecf001hy51c/)

__Requirements__:

- Total.js framework v4 (latest version)
- Node.js v14+

## Usage in Total.js apps

Total.js framework supports for support for __TMS__. First, you need to register `publish` and `subscribe` schemas. You can use raw JSON schemas that you store in the `/jsonschemas/` directory or use Total.js Schemas. TMS will transform all data according to the registered schemas.

#### Enable TMS

__`/config`__:

```config
allow_tms    : true
secret_tms   : your_secret_key
```

#### Register channels

You can use `definition` file e.g. `/definitions/tms.js` for registering channels.

__Register `Publish` channel__:

```js
// NEWPUBLISH('publish_name', 'JSON schema name OR Total.js schema name');

NEWPUBLISH('users_insert', 'Users');
NEWPUBLISH('users_update', 'Users');
NEWPUBLISH('users_remove', 'Users');

NEWPUBLISH('products_insert', 'Products');
NEWPUBLISH('products_update', 'Products');
NEWPUBLISH('products_remove', 'Products');
```

__Register `Subscribe` channel__:

```js
// NEWSUBSCRIBE('subscribe_name', 'JSON schema name OR Total.js schema name');

NEWSUBSCRIBE('users_insert', 'Users');
NEWSUBSCRIBE('users_update', 'Users');
NEWSUBSCRIBE('users_remove', 'Users');

NEWSUBSCRIBE('products_insert', 'Products');
NEWSUBSCRIBE('products_update', 'Products');
NEWSUBSCRIBE('products_remove', 'Products');
```

#### Usage in the code

```js
NEWSCHEMA('Users', function(schema) {

	schema.define('name', 'String(50)');

	schema.setInsert(function($, model) {

		model.id = UID();
		model.dtcreated = NOW;
		DBMS().insert('tbl_user', model).callback($.done());

		// !!! Publish example:
		// Sends the model via TMS to the integrator app
		PUBLISH('users_insert', model);

	});

	// !!! Subscribe example:
	// Receives data via TMS from the integrator app
	SUBSCRIBE('users_insert', function(model) {

		// Performs inserting
		EXEC('+Users --> insert', model, NOOP);

	});

});
```

