Total.js framework supports `LOADCONFIG(config_items)` method which loads configuration of the framework/app dynamically.

__Create a definition file `/definitions/func.js`:__

```js
// Loads app configuration from database
FUNC.refresh_config = function(callback) {
	DBMS().find('cl_config').fields('id,type,value').data(function(response) {

		// The method below expects Array Object { id:String, type:String, value: string }
		// Value is automatically converted to defined type by the framework
		// More in Total.js/Globals section
		LOADCONFIG(response);

		callback && callback();
	});
};

ON('ready', function() {

	// Loads configuration after the application is ready to use
	FUNC.refresh_config();

});

ON('service', function(counter) {

	// Configuration will be reloaded each 20 minutes
	if (counter % 20 === 0)
		FUNC.refresh_config();

});
```

__Table: `cl_config` in database__:

```sql
CREATE TABLE "public"."cl_config" (
	"id" varchar(30) NOT NULL,
	"type" varchar(10),
	"value" text,
	"name" varchar(50),                     -- human readable name
	"backup" text,                          -- backup of previous value
	"sortindex" int2 DEFAULT 0,
	"iseditable" bool DEFAULT false,        -- targeted for UI
	"ishidden" bool DEFAULT false,          -- targeted for UI
	"isremoved" bool DEFAULT false,
	"dtcreated" timestamp DEFAULT now(),
	"dtupdated" timestamp,
	PRIMARY KEY ("id")
);
```

__How to edit configuration on client-side?__

We have prepared UI component called [__j-Properties2__](https://componentator.com/components/j-properties2/) for editing of app configuration. You need to code only a logic for load/save.

### How to store `PREF` with the help of storing configuration?

```js
DEF.onPrefSave = function(data) {
	DBMS().modify('cl_config', { id: 'preferences', value: JSON.stringify(data), dtupdated: NOW }, true).id('preferences');
};

DEF.onPrefLoad = function(next) {
	DBMS().read('cl_config').where('id', 'preferences').fields('value').callback(function(err, response) {
		next((response ? (response.value || '').parseJSON(true) : null) || {});
	});
};
```

